Packages 
Package Description
com.vernalis.pdbconnector
This package contains the core KNIME-related classes for the PDB Connector webservice nodes
com.vernalis.pdbconnector.config
This package implements (non-KNIME related) classes used to define the query and report options supported by the PDB advanced search and custom report web services.
com.vernalis.pdbconnector.containers
This package contains classes for holding and parsing PDB heterogen details
com.vernalis.pdbconnector.nodes.combinequery
This package contains the classes for the Combine Advanced XML Query node
com.vernalis.pdbconnector.nodes.describehet
This package contains classes for the Describe Heterogens nodes
com.vernalis.pdbconnector.nodes.pdbconnector
This package contains the classes for the node implementations for the 2nd Generation PDB Connector node family
com.vernalis.pdbconnector.nodes.smilesquery
This package contains classes for the PDB SMILES Query node
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2
This package contains general utility classes for the new PDB Connector nodes
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.dialogcomponents
This package contains DialogComponents and their associated SettingsModels for the new PDB Connector nodes
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.dialogcomponents.suggester
This package contains Suggester implementations for the new PDB Connector nodes
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.dialogcomponents.swing
This package contains Swing components for the new PDB Connector nodes
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.graphql
This package contains classes to define a GraphQL query
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.graphql.result
This package contains classes and annotations to define and parse the results of a GraphQL query
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.nodes
This package is the root for the new PDB Connector nodes.
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.nodes.build
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Query Builder node
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.nodes.combine
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Combine Queries node
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.nodes.execute
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Query Executor node
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.nodes.load
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Read Query node
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.nodes.loopstart
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Queries Table Loop Start node
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.nodes.save
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Write Query node
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.nodes.totable
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Queries To Table node
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.ports
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Query Port Type
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.query
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Query definitions
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.query.chemical
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Chemical Query type
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.query.sequence
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Sequence Query types
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.query.structsim
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Structural Similarity Query type
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.query.text.dialog
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Text Query type dialog components and models
com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.query.text.fields
This package contains the classes for the PDB Connector Text Query field definitions
com.vernalis.rcsb.io.helpers  
com.vernalis.rcsb.io.nodes.manip  
com.vernalis.rcsb.io.nodes.source  
com.vernalis.rest
This package contains classes to run simple RESTful GET and POST requests, and also to run them in separate Threads
